    "rich_text_DBkXF7": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_GtgCfx": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How AirVape Dropshipping Works",
            "heading_size": "h3",
            "heading_html_tag": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_UBHr7r": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>AirVape dropshipping allows approved partners to promote and sell selected products without stocking inventory themselves.</p><p>Once you receive an order from your customer, you submit the order details to our team for fulfillment. We then process, pack, and ship the order directly to the end customer on your behalf.</p><p>This model helps approved partners expand product offerings while reducing inventory risk and operational overhead.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_GtgCfx",
        "text_UBHr7r"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "full_width": true,
        "content_alignment": "mx-auto",
        "text_alignment": "text-left",
        "content_width": "normal",
        "background_color": "",
        "text_color": "",
        "heading_color": ""
      }
    },
    "rich_text_GQRktq": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_nW8erU": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Dropshipping Process",
            "heading_size": "h3",
            "heading_html_tag": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_jtraKy": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3><strong>1. Partner Approval</strong></h3><p>Your business is reviewed and approved for the AirVape dropshipping program.</p><h3><strong>2. Product Listing</strong></h3><p>Approved products are listed on your website, store, marketplace, or other approved sales channels.</p><h3><strong>3. Customer Order Received</strong></h3><p>You collect the customer order and payment through your own platform.</p><h3><strong>4. Order Submission</strong></h3><p>You submit the complete paid order details, including accurate shipping information, to our team for fulfillment.</p><h3><strong>5. Order Processing and Dispatch</strong></h3><p>After order confirmation and acceptance by our team, we process, pack, and dispatch the order.</p><h3><strong>6. Tracking Shared</strong></h3><p>Tracking information is shared after shipment so you can update your customer.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_nW8erU",
        "text_jtraKy"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "full_width": true,
        "content_alignment": "mx-auto",
        "text_alignment": "text-left",
        "content_width": "normal",
        "background_color": "",
        "text_color": "",
        "heading_color": ""
      }
    },
    "rich_text_4T4naT": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_3GAQgG": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Order Flow From Placement to Fulfillment",
            "heading_size": "h3",
            "heading_html_tag": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_RGxFxm": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The partner is responsible for collecting the end-customer order and payment through their own sales channel.</p><p>After receiving the order, the partner submits the complete order details to us. Fulfillment begins only after:</p><ul><li>Order confirmation</li><li>Order acceptance by our team</li><li>Product availability verification</li></ul><p>Once approved, we process, pack, and dispatch the order directly to the customer on the partner’s behalf.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_3GAQgG",
        "text_RGxFxm"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "full_width": true,
        "content_alignment": "mx-auto",
        "text_alignment": "text-left",
        "content_width": "normal",
        "background_color": "",
        "text_color": "",
        "heading_color": ""
      }
    },
    "rich_text_TWzcNm": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_HVYaU4": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Why Partner With AirVape for Dropshipping?",
            "heading_size": "h3",
            "heading_html_tag": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_nxG8Xh": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3><strong>No Need to Hold Inventory</strong></h3><p>Approved partners can sell AirVape products without purchasing and storing stock in advance.</p><h3><strong>Direct Fulfillment</strong></h3><p>We handle order processing, packing, and shipping directly to the end customer after order approval.</p><h3><strong>Product Expansion</strong></h3><p>Dropshipping makes it easier for partners to expand their product range without increasing warehousing complexity.</p><h3><strong>Flexible Selling Channels</strong></h3><p>Approved partners may market and sell AirVape products through their own approved sales channels, subject to reseller terms and policy compliance.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_HVYaU4",
        "text_nxG8Xh"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "full_width": true,
        "content_alignment": "mx-auto",
        "text_alignment": "text-left",
        "content_width": "normal",
        "background_color": "",
        "text_color": "",
        "heading_color": ""
      }
    },
    "rich_text_XXknih": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_Uz4VzV": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Shipping Information",
            "heading_size": "h3",
            "heading_html_tag": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_B8XpxF": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3><strong>Shipping Times</strong></h3><p>Shipping timelines vary based on:</p><ul><li>Stock availability</li><li>Order volume</li><li>Destination country</li><li>Courier service</li><li>Customs procedures</li></ul><p>Processing and transit times are <strong>estimates only</strong> and are <strong>not guaranteed unless agreed in writing</strong>.</p><h3><strong>Shipping Regions</strong></h3><p>We ship to selected domestic and international regions where courier service is available.</p><p>Some destinations may be restricted due to:</p><ul><li>Shipping limitations</li><li>Customs regulations</li><li>Commercial policy</li><li>Product restrictions in certain markets</li></ul><p>Exact shipping availability can be confirmed based on the destination and order details.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_Uz4VzV",
        "text_B8XpxF"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "full_width": true,
        "content_alignment": "mx-auto",
        "text_alignment": "text-left",
        "content_width": "normal",
        "background_color": "",
        "text_color": "",
        "heading_color": ""
      }
    },
    "rich_text_YJt99F": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_XaicCk": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Returns and Refunds",
            "heading_size": "h3",
            "heading_html_tag": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_ccdBni": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Returns and refunds for dropshipping orders are handled according to our approved return policy.</p><p>Claims for <strong>damaged, defective, or incorrect items</strong> must be reported within the approved claim period and must include <strong>photo or video evidence</strong> for review.</p><p>No return, refund, or replacement will be processed without prior approval.</p><h3><strong>Return Restrictions</strong></h3><p>Not all returns are accepted.</p><p>The following may be rejected:</p><ul><li>Unauthorized returns</li><li>Used items</li><li>Customer-damaged items</li><li>Claims submitted outside the approved reporting period</li></ul><p>Refund or replacement approval remains subject to inspection and policy compliance.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_XaicCk",
        "text_ccdBni"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "full_width": true,
        "content_alignment": "mx-auto",
